 Riazor]], [[A Coru\u00f1a]], Spain || align=center | 9 || {{fb|BEL}} || align=center | 3\u20130 || align=center | 5\u20130 || rowspan=2|2010 FIFA World Cup qualification\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align: center;\"|4\n| 14 October 2009 || [[Bilino Polje]], [[Zenica]], Bosnia and Herzegovina || align=center | 12 || {{fb|BIH}} || align=center | 1\u20130 || align=center | 5\u20132\n|-\n!scope=row style=\"text-align: center;\"|5\n| 13 June 2016 || [[Stadium Municipal]], [[Toulouse]], France || align=center | 78 || {{fb|CZE}} || align=center | 1\u20130 || align=center | 1\u20130 || [[UEFA Euro 2016]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n[[File:Piqu\u00e9.jpg|thumb|upright|Piqu\u00e9 celebrating victory after receiving his medal for winning the [[2009 UEFA Champions League Final]]]]\n\n'''Manchester United'''\n*[[Premier League]]: [[2007\u201308 Premier League|2007\u201308]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/players/2737/Gerard-Piqu\u00e9/overview |title=Gerard Piqu\u00e9: Overview |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=17 April 2018}}</ref>\n*[[FA Community Shield]]: [[2007 FA Community Shield|2007]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6929113.stm |title=Chelsea 1\u20131 Man Utd |first=Caroline |last=Cheese |work=BBC Sport |date=5 August 2007 |accessdate=17 April 2018}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Champions League]]: [[2007\u201308 UEFA Champions League|2007\u201308]]<ref>{{cite web |title=How brilliant is Barcelona defender Gerard Piqu\u00e9?|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2432740.html |publisher=UEFA |date=3 October 2018 |accessdate=15 March 2019}}</ref>\n\n'''Barcelona'''<ref name=FCBprofile/>\n*[[La Liga]]: [[2008\u201309 La Liga|2008\u201309]], [[2009\u201310 La Liga|2009\u201310]], [[2010\u201311 La Liga|2010\u201311]], [[2012\u201313 La Liga|2012\u201313]], [[2014\u201315 La Liga|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 La Liga|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 La Liga|2017\u201318]], [[2018\u201319 La Liga|2018\u201319]]\n*[[Copa del Rey